parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to lose acceleration, shut off, or downshift unexpectedly, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses acceleration
a grinding metal noise emerges from the engine
the check engine warning light is illuminated
the vehicle shuts off
and the transmission fails to engage gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended downshifting can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle downshifts unexpectedly
the vehicle shuts off
and the check engine warning light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Ignoring recall issues can lead to serious safety consequences, including accidents or injuries, as well as financial losses for the vehicle owner.
symptoms: Dealerships or manufacturers fail to acknowledge or repair recall issues
leading to ongoing problems with the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of a crash, potentially resulting in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates on the dashboard
the airbag fails to deploy in a crash
the seatbelt warning light illuminates on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seatbelt system can lead to the failure of the seatbelt to properly restrain the occupant in the event of a crash, potentially resulting in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The seatbelt warning light illuminates on the dashboard
the seatbelt fails to properly restrain the occupant in a crash
the airbag warning light illuminates on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn, making it challenging to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of vehicle control.
symptoms: The steering wheel becomes very difficult to turn
the vehicle has a loss of powertrain
the power steering does not function
the vehicle is hard to control
the steering wheel seizes.
